      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Júnior</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Benhur-RedQueen-Brazil.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7a/Benhur-RedQueen-Brazil.jpg/300px-Benhur-RedQueen-Brazil.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7a/Benhur-RedQueen-Brazil.jpg/450px-Benhur-RedQueen-Brazil.jpg 1.5x, /images/7/7a/Benhur-RedQueen-Brazil.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Benhur-RedQueen-Brazil.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Junior <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Júnior</b>,<br />\na Brazilian computer scientist and software engineer holding a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bachelor%27s_degree\">Bachelor's degree</a> in computer science from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Universidade_Salgado_de_Oliveira\">Universidade Salgado de Oliveira</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Gon%C3%A7alo,_Rio_de_Janeiro\">São Gonçalo, Rio de Janeiro</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. As computer chess programmer, Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Júnio is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/RedQueen\" title=\"RedQueen\">RedQueen</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ben-Hur_Carlos_Vieira_Langoni_Junior&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36722\">Problem using XBoard + Polyglot + Zippy on FICS</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ben-Hur Carlos Langoni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 15, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/XBoard\" title=\"XBoard\">XBoard</a>, <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Free_Internet_Chess_Server&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Free Internet Chess Server (page does not exist)\">Free Internet Chess Server</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37748\">Improving evaluation of passed pawns</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ben-Hur Carlos Langoni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 22, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Passed Pawn\">Passed Pawn</a>, <a href=\"/Candidate_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Candidate Passed Pawn\">Candidate Passed Pawn</a>, <a href=\"/Unstoppable_Passer\" title=\"Unstoppable Passer\">Unstoppable Passer</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=38808\">Questions on SMP search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ben-Hur Carlos Langoni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 21, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50493\">Most wanted missing features for a chess GUI</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ben-Hur Carlos Langoni</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 14, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ben-Hur_Carlos_Vieira_Langoni_Junior&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/bhlangonijr/\">Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Junior | LinkedIn</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/bhlangonijr\">bhlangonijr (Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Junior) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/redqueenchess/\">RedQueen Chess Engine website</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://redqueenchess.sourceforge.net/\">RedQueen | Chess Engine</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ben-Hur_Carlos_Vieira_Langoni_Junior&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Junior @ <a href=\"/ICT_2010\" title=\"ICT 2010\">ICT 2010</a>, Image by <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a>,  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessvibes.com/?q=reports/rybka-wins-10th-ict-in-leiden\">Rybka wins 10th ICT in Leiden</a> by <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessvibes.com/\">ChessVibes</a>, May 31, 2010</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://contactout.com/Ben-HurCarlos-VieiraLangoniJunior-26242912\">Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Junior | Software Engineer @ Radiant IQ</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://redqueenchess.sourceforge.net/\">RedQueen | Chess Engine</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>]\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228230649\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4758-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228230649 and revision id 9004\n -->\n"
